  <name>COSMIC Web Apps</name>
  <summary>WAM - Web App Manager written with love and libcosmic. </summary>
  <description>
    <p>Web App Manager for Cosmic desktop written with love and libcosmic. Allow you to simply create web applications from given url working inside separate window of your browser of choice.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Fast and easy to use.</li>
	<li>Allow you to create simple web apps from given url.</li>
	<li>Papirus icon pack installer in app for icon chooser.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">org.cosmic.Wam.desktop</launchable>
  <icon type="remote" height="256" width="256">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/elevenhsoft/cosmic-wam/master/data/org.cosmic.Wam.png</icon>
